@startuml
title 发送消息时序图

actor "用户A" as UserA
actor "用户B" as UserB

participant "前端" as Frontend
participant "WebSocket\n服务器" as WebSocket
participant "消息服务" as MessageService
participant "RabbitMQ" as RabbitMQ
participant "数据库" as Database

UserA -> Frontend: 输入消息并发送
Frontend -> WebSocket: 通过WebSocket发送消息
WebSocket -> MessageService: 调用消息服务
MessageService -> RabbitMQ: 将消息放入队列
MessageService -> Database: 存储消息
RabbitMQ -> WebSocket: 推送消息到接收方
WebSocket -> Frontend: 推送消息到用户B前端
Frontend -> UserB: 显示消息

@enduml